#, no-c-format
msgid "camera"
msgstr "相機"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "photo"
msgstr "相片"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module allows you to configure support for your digital camera."
msgstr "這個模組讓您設定對您的數位相機的支援。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Add</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>新增</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to select the camera's model and the port it is connected "
"to on your computer (&eg; USB, Serial). If your camera does not appear in "
"the list of <guilabel>Supported Cameras</guilabel>, go to the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.gphoto.org\">GPhoto web site</ulink> for a possible update."
msgstr ""
"點擊這個按鈕來選取相機的型號以及它所連線到的連接埠（如 USB 或 Serial）。如果"
"您的相機不在<guilabel>支援的照相機</guilabel>列表中，請試試看去<ulink url="
"\"http://www.gphoto.org\">GPhoto 的網站</ulink>看看有沒有更新。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Test"
msgstr "測試"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to test the connection to the selected camera."
msgstr "點擊這個按鈕來測試所選相機的連線。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "移除"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected camera from the list."
msgstr "從列表中移除所選的相機。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "設定"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to change the configuration of the selected camera. The "
"availability of this feature and the contents of the Configuration dialog "
"depend on the camera model."
msgstr ""
"點擊這個按鈕來調整所選相機的設定。依相機型號這個功能可能無法使用，且設定對話"
"框所提供的內容也有可能不同。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "資訊"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to view a summary of the current status of the selected "
"camera. The availability of this feature and the contents of the Information "
"dialog depend on the camera model."
msgstr ""
"點擊這個按鈕來檢視所選相機的目前狀態的摘要。依相機型號這個功能可能無法使用，"
"且資訊對話框的內容也有可能不同。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to cancel the current camera operation."
msgstr "點擊這個按鈕來取消目前的相機操作。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and download images from the digital camera, enter "
"<userinput>camera:/</userinput> in &konqueror;&apos;s or &dolphin;&apos;s "
"location bar."
msgstr ""
"要從數位相機檢視或下載影像，請在 &konqueror; 或 &dolphin; 的位置列中輸入 "
"<userinput>camera:/</userinput>。"
